item.title: Videos of Google IO 2011 – Android Tracks of Day One
item.description: Google IOis currently taking place in San Franciscoand for everybody who could not attend Googlelive streamed quite some sessions. In the following you can see the videos which are currently published: [youtube OxzucwjFEEs] As an Android developer I am very interested in the Android sessions as you can imagine. So the following the next video first covers advaced topics of android development. [youtube twmuBbC_oB8] The next video discusses business modelsthat you as a developer can use to monetize your app.
